  "commit_message": "ci: drop redundant OIDC_AUDIENCE — the action derives it from API_BASE_URL\n\nThe sbomify action's obtain_sbomify_token_via_oidc() falls back to\ndefault_audience_for(api_base_url) when OIDC_AUDIENCE is unset: production\n(app.sbomify.com / no base URL) -> sbomify.com, and any other deployment ->\nthe API_BASE_URL hostname (stage.sbomify.com for the staging jobs). So all four\nOIDC_AUDIENCE lines were redundant. The staging jobs keep API_BASE_URL, which\nnow drives both the upload target and the derive",
